snippet.title: QBz Gameplay (All Game Modes Included)
snippet.description:
QBz was one of the coolest game ever released by Skunk Studios, also the maker of Varmintz Deluxe.

So, I have made a gameplay video of QBz featuring all modes of the game.

Download QBz here:
https://youtu.be/JzPHN8zKVmw

ENJOY THE GAMEPLAY :D

LIKE.SHARE.SUBSCRIBE | AJ VIDEOS

Checkout the gears and gadgets I use and my recommendations. These are my affiliate links. If you purchase through these links, I will get a very small commissions for recommending this. If you have urgent requirements to buy this and you don't have money to donate it to me, then I would highly recommend you to SUBSCRIBE my channel and by through my personal links. If you have any other product you wanna purchase in the near future, please ping me via email or comments and I would respond to you at the earliest. Here you go then:

Samsung A52s Mobile: https://amzn.to/4apsWub  -  Currently Unavailable
Cosmic Byte Firefly Mechanical Keyboard: https://amzn.to/42pQIV3   -  Currently Unavailable 
Sony 1000 XM4: https://amzn.to/4g1GfSF   -  Buy if available for Rs. 18k 
Sony 1000 XM5: https://amzn.to/3Ed3wUn   -  My future headphone if current one goes kaput 
Galaxy Watch 7 44m LTE: https://amzn.to/4gWR3mr   -  best buy if available for Rs. 28k 
Logitech M171 Mouse: https://amzn.to/3Cg7lHW   -  okish mouse, go for OG M186 instead 
Logitech M186 Mouse: https://amzn.to/4hcBhnm   -  a good mouse 
Asus TuF A15 Upper tier: https://amzn.to/4jopRic   -  mine is 2020 version with R7 1650 GDDR6, this is 4070 which is a beast coupled with R9 
Asus TuF A15 Mid Tier: https://amzn.to/4jk3muB   -  R7 + 4060 variant, can run most of the games in very high graphics 
Asus TuF A15 Low Tier: https://amzn.to/4h01xl0   -  R7 + 3050, okish laptop 
Asus TuF A15 Very Low Tier: https://amzn.to/4gWLHaX   -  R7 + 2050, ok laptop 
Wacom Tablet: https://amzn.to/3Cb4WOP   -  a good pen tablet for drawing and teaching 
Macbook Pro M3 36GB Ram  -  Work Laptop: https://amzn.to/40E4YIf   -  great for utility and enterprise
